channel.title: Spirit Collapse/Decomposition - Hern [Genre?]
channel.description:
Here's a new track from my upcoming album, "Health." I've been taking a much more ambient direction on this one, but this final track kind of diverts from the more low key sound of the rest of the album. I'm not quite sure what genre this (I know it falls under the blanket "electronic" and has some experimental/ambient elements, but besides that I'm not sure).
Link is here: https://soundcloud.com/hernmusicofficial/decomposition
Hope you guys enjoy, constructive criticism is welcomed as always. Album will be coming soon.
